            <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
              <div class="button">
                <a target="_blank" href="https://www.gofundme.com/help-kassiopes-eye-care-center" class="btn btn-warning btn-lg"><%= t(:support) %></a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-2">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12 arrow text-center">
          <a href="#issue">
            <i class="fa fa-angle-down pulse" style="color: black; margin-bottom: 15px;"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>


      <div id="issue">
        <div class="container box">
          <h2>What is the issue</h2>
          <h4>1.000.000.000 people suffer from refractive error!</h4>
          <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="challenge scrollReveal feature col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
                <%= image_tag "rub.svg", class: "logo-homepage", alt: "Rubikube"%>
                <p>Every daily task becomes a challenge!</p>
              </div>

              <div class="read scrollReveal feature col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
                <%= image_tag "read-book-logo.svg", class: "logo-homepage", alt: "Books"%>
                <p>Cataract is the first cause for blindness in the world!</p>
              </div>

              <div class="glasses scrollReveal feature col-md-4 col-xs-12">
                <%= image_tag "glasses.svg", class: "logo-homepage", alt: "Glasses"%>
                <p>Glasses are not affordable!</p>
              </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>


      </div>

      <div id="action" class="box">
        <h2>Our project this year in Ahmedabad India</h2>
        <div class="container-fluid">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="next-to-photo-text col-md-7 col-sm-8 col-xs-12">
              <ul>
                <li>Our project will take place between January and March 2018</li>
                <li>Continue to carry out its eye tests and distribute glasses</li>
                <li>Offer cataract surgery to the communities associated with Manav Sadhna</li>
                <li>Deepen local doctors’ knowledge about pathologies associated to eyes</li>
                <li>Help create a center in order to teach doctors how to perform cataract surgeries through the Lotus Eye Clinic’s ophtalmologists</li>
                <li>Initiate a project that is both socially and economically sustainable</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="action-img text-center col-md-5 col-sm-4">
              <%= image_tag "groupe-enfants.jpg", class: "hidden-xs", alt: "Indian girl"%>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div id="us" class="box">

        <div class="container-fluid">
          <h2>Let's talk about us !</h2>
          <div class="row">

            <div class="us-img text-center col-sm-5">
              <%= image_tag "matt.png", class: "img-rounded hidden-xs" %>
            </div>


            <div class="us-text next-to-photo-text col-sm-7">
              <ul>
                <li>Kassiopé is a non-lucrative association aimed at offering free eye care to the most disabled</li>
                <li>Two of us, having already been to India and taught in one of the schools near the Gandhi Ashram, imagined a project of offering free eye tests and glasses to the numerous students, especially children</li>
                <li>We all share the ambition : Travel to India, together, for the purpose of offering to children a decent quality of life, beginning by a suitable eyesight.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

      </div> <!--Close id us -->

      <div class="space">

      </div>





